{"tid":1853703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友喺新蒲崗藥行買咗Skater MSKP5口罩，好⋯貴","createTime":"2020-01-31T06:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T19:23:26.000Z","uid":230019,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"22bd5c1f21d686c724e746dc5b0797da6c407be6","tid":1853703,"uid":230019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T06:29:08.000Z","msg":"頭先一點半嘅時候朋友經過新蒲崗呢間叫宏輝中西藥行嘅舖頭買咗包Skater MSKP5嘅口罩，盛惠 $60/10隻，非獨立包裝，本身諗住再買多幾包，但都係停一停，冷靜下先。<br />\n佢叫我幫佢Post上嚟問下大家有無聽過，因為就咁上網都睇唔到咩資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃圈圈住個男人就話係日本返貨嘅，朋友入到去就見到有白色同呢款黑色嘅賣緊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1GaNv3q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1GaNv3q.png&h=65dc04bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8MYCTgQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8MYCTgQ.png&h=b50431e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U0AhTg3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU0AhTg3.png&h=4e9ce63a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZE2gpoX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZE2gpoX.png&h=0f1087c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ouDvtQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FouDvtQQ.png&h=7344df3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 呢間舖頭上個禮拜有賣永寶呢款口罩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chiZ6C8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FchiZ6C8.png&h=775f494b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"298adecd3083f513428645278758e450286fd538","tid":1853703,"uid":230019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T06:32:33.000Z","msg":"輕輕推下"},{"pid":"000e93f440afedeaa12daef5d430134aebc6d0c6","tid":1853703,"uid":33728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T06:34:22.000Z","msg":"假"},{"pid":"84257ac8d92c7d708833e5e666cab20df14